    ORDER BY [p].[DateCreated] DESC
) AS [t]

LEFT JOIN [Products] AS [p1] ON [p0].[Id] = [p1].[CategoryId]
WHERE [p].[Status] = 1
ORDER BY [p].[DateCreated] DESC, [p].[Id], [p0].[Id]" (0723d8ff)

    OFFSET @__p_0 ROWS FETCH NEXT @__p_1 ROWS ONLY
) AS [t]
INNER JOIN [Products] AS [p0] ON [t].[ProductId] = [p0].[Id]
INNER JOIN [ProductCategories] AS [p1] ON [p0].[CategoryId] = [p1].[Id]
LEFT JOIN [Products] AS [p2] ON [p1].[Id] = [p2].[CategoryId]
ORDER BY [t].[DateCreated] DESC, [t].[Id], [p0].[Id], [p1].[Id]" (0723d8ff)

    SELECT TOP(@__p_0) [p].[Id], [p].[Author], [p].[CategoryId], [p].[Content], [p].[DateCreated], [p].[DateModified], [p].[Description], [p].[HomeFlag], [p].[HotFlag], [p].[Image], [p].[Name], [p].[OriginalPrice], [p].[Price], [p].[PromotionPrice], [p].[Publisher], [p].[SeoAlias], [p].[SeoDescription], [p].[SeoKeywords], [p].[SeoPageTitle], [p].[SortOrder], [p].[Status], [p].[Tags], [p].[ViewCount]

    WHERE ([p].[Status] = 1) AND ([p].[HotFlag] = CAST(1 AS bit))
    ORDER BY [p].[DateCreated] DESC
) AS [t]
INNER JOIN [ProductCategories] AS [p0] ON [t].[CategoryId] = [p0].[Id]
